snippet.title: Best VGSFX 01 - Pokemon - Healing Sound
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame sound effects. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gameboy
Pokemon (1996)
Healing Sound
